---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<aside
  class="not-prose relative left-1/2 my-12 w-[min(92vw,960px)] -translate-x-1/2 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-brand-border/60 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-soft/80 via-white to-brand-soft/30 p-6 shadow-xs transition hover-lift sm:p-8"
  aria-labelledby="community-tutorial-title"
>
  <!-- Decorative soft glow background -->
  <div class="absolute -right-16 -top-16 -z-10 h-32 w-32 rounded-full bg-brand-muted/20 blur-2xl"></div>

  <div class="flex flex-col justify-between min-w-0">
    <div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full bg-brand-soft px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-brand-text border border-brand-border/30 shadow-xs">
          <Icon class="h-3.5 w-3.5" name="bx:bx-award" />
          社区推荐教程
        </span>
      </div>
      
      <a
        id="community-tutorial-title"
        class="group mt-3 inline-flex items-start gap-1.5 text-lg font-bold leading-snug text-slate-900 transition hover:text-brand-text"
        href="https://www.dujin.org/23773.html"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        <span class="underline decoration-slate-200 decoration-2 underline-offset-4 transition group-hover:decoration-brand-border">
          一分钟部署零成本、开源且原生支持 AI Agent 的个人笔记 EdgeEver
        </span>
        <Icon class="mt-1 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-slate-400 transition group-hover:text-brand-text group-hover:translate-x-0.5 group-hover:-translate-y-0.5" name="bx:bx-link-external" />
      </a>
      
      <p class="mt-3 text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
        由独立博主「缙哥哥」精心撰写的第三方中文图文教程（内容由其独立维护）。在此特别感谢他在项目早期提供了许多宝贵建议与测试环境支持！
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-slate-100/60 flex items-center justify-end">
      <a
        href="https://www.dujin.org/23773.html"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-semibold text-brand transition hover:text-brand-hover hover:underline"
      >
        阅读教程 <Icon class="h-4 w-4" name="bx:bx-right-arrow-alt" />
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</aside>


